data.description: This cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bath home in the sought-after So Broadway Heights neighborhood offers a warm and inviting atmosphere. The new interior paint and hardwood floors contribute to its charm, while the gas range adds a modern touch to the kitchen. The large primary bedroom  with its own outside entrance provides both convenience and privacy. The fully fenced yard, complete with a garden area and playground, enhances the outdoor living experience. Recent upgrades, including copper plumbing and a new furnace, ensure both comfort and efficiency. Notably, appliances, television mounts, and window coverings are thoughtfully included, making this home move-in ready and well-equipped. Close to shopping and restaurants!
